sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import axios from 'axios' function RowDetails({fullname,nic,phone,email,check_in,check_out,no_of_rooms,totalmember,payment,Id , OnDelete }) { return ( {fullname} {nic} {phone} {email} {check_in} {check_out} {no_of_rooms} {totalmember} {payment} OnDelete(Id)}> ) } export default RowDetails
